                            <comment id="34741" author="luke" created="Tue, 15 Apr 2008 04:06:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the report. We should probably add an AuthenticationTrustResolver to the wrapper (or HttpSCIF) to allow it to determine that the user is anonymous and the context should not be saved.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="34989" author="luke" created="Tue, 22 Apr 2008 00:23:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve added a check for anonymous authentication to HttpSessionContextIntegrationFilter.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
